<br>
I suggest:<br>
<br>
Use Charred Guardian instead of Testiment. (-1 WIS, -10 Mana, +10 AC)<br>
<br>
Use Froglok Crown instead of Nightshade. (-5 WIS, +11 AC)<br>
<br>
Use Mammoth instead Kunzar Cloak. (+2 WIS, Same AC)<br>
<br>
Use NEW (AC:8, +3 WIS, -3DEX) sleves in SoV) (+8 AC) NOTE: This is a pretty easy to get item so should be cheap soon.  Since they are dropable you should start seeing them a auction in a week or two. Non-rare spawn drop.<br>
<br>
Using that setup you will loose 4 Wisdom and 10 mana Over-all (putting you at around 196.)  But you will gain +29 base AC.<br>
<br>
In the future you could consider adding Medicine totem for Kerran Toy, and gain back 5 WIS for 199.<br>
<br>
Just realize that you will never see a difference in your mana pool between 190 WIS, and 200 WIS... you WILL however see a difference with 29 more AC.<br>
